{"tid":731053,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇 陣式係死，人係生 既講法？","createTime":"2018-07-06T01:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T12:34:56.000Z","uid":176368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcf697005b5988a4af3b80f89c72163a090dc7e","tid":731053,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉先，睇下各位其他意見<br />\n<br />\n陣式幫教練排陣 同規範球員既企位<br />\n唔同陣式對應唔同情況<br />\n例如 前後左右4個進攻球員對大巴<br />\n所以唔變陣=死，變陣=生<br />\n<br />\n反證：庸才教練淨係識換人唔換陣<br />\n陣式唔變 球員都冇咩作為"},{"pid":"14ba7a93ebbbb7285699bed07550aca3f9abd093","tid":731053,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"享利同哥帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370965c66fe1e11e37efcf659b06d698945f8324","tid":731053,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14ba7a93ebbbb7285699bed07550aca3f9abd093","tid":731053,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"享利同哥帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"冇follow佢地，係點？"},{"pid":"7a099977f39cd76358d06a1a24bc6d744ef04240","tid":731053,"uid":91636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"嚴格黎講出咩陣教練就講埋點走位要做啲乜<br />\n有啲會俾自由度你自己發揮<br />\n有啲要你一定要跟佢個套<br />\n有時球員知教練個套唔掂自己去馬唔服從<br />\n賽前準確得好/有自由度/唔服從=人係生<br />\n但唔服又唔係大佬就可能要踢後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6494720f4bc79ef0bfcf06b640b88f20c7ef0f52","tid":731053,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"陣式令到人生<br />\n完"},{"pid":"1619d8abcf9c023a0086f7ea8fa04f882dfe2ec7","tid":731053,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6494720f4bc79ef0bfcf06b640b88f20c7ef0f52","tid":731053,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:05: